                            jcr:primaryType="cpp:Element"
                            sling:resourceType="composum/pages/components/element/textimage"
                            text="&lt;p>The Composum Nodes module provides the core API fo all Composum modules. The Console framework is part of the Nodes module and builds the base for a set of useful administration and development tools for the Sling Framework which are bundled with the Compsum Nodes module. The console framework is also used by some Composum extensions and the Assets module to implement and integrate their management user interfaces.&lt;/p>">
