                            text="&lt;p>The Composum Browser gives you the ability to explore your Sling repository with a lot of useful features:&lt;/p>&lt;p>&lt;ul>&lt;li>repository tree with configurable filters&lt;/li>&lt;li>node creation / deletion / move / reorder&lt;/li>&lt;li>property manipulation&lt;/li>&lt;li>binary data upload / download&lt;/li>&lt;li>component rendering and asset view&lt;/li>&lt;li>template based queries with history&lt;/li>&lt;li>JSON view, download and upload&lt;/li>&lt;li>ACL view and manipulation&lt;/li>&lt;li>Groovy script execution&lt;/li>&lt;/ul>&lt;/p>"
